NFL games are very suitable for our purposes because : ( 1 ) two online exchanges and one online prediction contest already exist that provide data on both information markets and the opinions of self-identified experts for the same set of games ; ( 2 ) the popularity of NFL games in the United States provides natural incentives for people to participate in information markets and/or the contest , which increases liquidity of information markets and improves the quality and number of opinions in the contest ; ( 3 ) intense media coverage and analysis of the profiles and strengths 